Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好刺眼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要和哈咪、大家建立聯繫，心連心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,心連心的聯繫究竟是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天氣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我考慮下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我再去海邊，我會不會尖叫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要再說這了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？他們都離開了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧。。來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等。等等。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快點換這件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，我們一起去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是好朋友，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。。是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將接受任何提程至今天下午
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將為他們評分和決定誰是贏家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還有，今年的獎品是。。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Spoon 杯蛋糕一年劵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我不參加，我將讓那群女的失望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，去年的贏家，王子，將會是今年的評審
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,王。。。王子前輩！！！評審？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她也燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮，我們盡力而為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,第24話\N完成與沙之哈咪的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爲了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想聽他們的應該不會有事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果發生什麽事，第一時間找哈咪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她。。根本沒當一回事。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我們應該做個吸引每個人的沙雕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮，你認為哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要巨大的漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也認為這是好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,漢堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這看起來好像蒲团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,奏，那你想要的是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想的是。。。。蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你每次都做蛋糕，所以說，今天我們做漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,漢堡不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那。。那麼扒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那，牛乳酒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麽？不行，不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕和漢堡！？ 那個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，，，兩者聽起來都不錯。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能告訴我們嗎？你們想做的沙雕是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是是。。是漢。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，是蛋。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們將會做些什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？！ 哈咪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，是只貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,24號，貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,誒，不是的。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等下過來拿你們的名卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,漢堡。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕。。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈，我是模特兒，好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係，哈咪也是很好的選擇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然我們還沒能決定好呢，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那。。我過去拿名卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,響。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮太為我們著想了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她一直都贊成我們的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她并沒有自己的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太認真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我還在想，她會不會叫我奏啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我們會彼此拉近距離的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，艾蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你又在幻想了。。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓她這麼稱呼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該強迫她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是哈咪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮是根據自己的決定跟隨我們\N所以我們只能等待和相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,誒，她們的名？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，響和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但怎麼沒見你這樣稱呼她們的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我害怕她們不喜歡我這樣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,響和奏不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,賽蓮你過度擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是。。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你們一定能成為最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你把話說得太簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在大調島里，我唯一的朋友只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,賽蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一起唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一起唱比較有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪，我能和其他人成為朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你就把他們當成是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我談話時沒任何保留
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就把她們當成是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,當成是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是猩猩，不是人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫吸引人群注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可不是讓群眾嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我採用你人魚的意見，所以讓我決定那個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,其實呢，那個猩猩好難看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，別躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋，笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看起來玩的很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我加入嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一起打架，一起笑讓人覺得好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是配合蒼太的級別而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你這個笨蛋，等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他們兩個玩的毫不保留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽我射不到你？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們毫不保留？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我打不到你，爲什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是玩的開心?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她們兩個人的名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他們兩個人的名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,響和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,響。。。奏。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就把她們當成我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪。。。。哈咪。。。。。哈咪。。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我說不出她們的名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,把名卡放上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們再做過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是我毀了，就讓我弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦，別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是朋友嘛，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有你一人在擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你失敗了，你就改變你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽這裡不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成為你們的朋友，但我該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於說出你的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的。。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是。。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,誰理會你做錯事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們約你過來這是想更瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起做著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都是互相幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你只需告訴我們你想要什麽，艾蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起談很多事情，一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我們會爭吵，但我們每次都會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,賽蓮，一起唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一起做事會更開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一起。。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要瞭解你們，成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你們三人會成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,響，沒尾巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好盡責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！爸爸，我做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,pat, pat, pat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,全部人都玩得好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是賽蓮？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,字牌（24號--貓【哈咪】）\N這是沙之哈咪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,音符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小調島三重唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不會的到音符的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,BASSDRUM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這音符是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧，負向音調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,負向音調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧，負向音調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才全部人還很開心的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,奪去他們的快樂時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,LETS PLAY PRECURE MODULATION
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈奏的是狂野音調~旋律天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈奏的是柔和音調~節奏天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,指尖彈奏的是靈魂音調~節拍天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,共鳴吧！我們的組曲音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,組曲光之美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,消滅那些光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,負向音調
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把那些沙雕破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全部人的沙雕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,節拍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,節拍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,賽蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,後悔成為光之美少女已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,誰後悔成為光之美少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我身邊有旋律和節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她們打從心底接受我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我身邊有珍貴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我心裡的節拍無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你不幫她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雙吉他杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,索利，這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,CHANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,MIRACLE BELLTIER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧，美利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,FANTASTIC BELLTIER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧，法利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧，音調之環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 HEARTFUL BEAT ROCK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 MUSIC RONDO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,3拍子！ 1.。2.。3.。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,FINALE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很快就能完成幸福旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,豈有此理，賽蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你會。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的冠軍是25號Kumai，海豚沙雕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,玩的好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蝸牛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是寄生蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,難道。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕這。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，我並不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艾蓮，你好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,誒，我不會原諒你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起去慶典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.32,0:23:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽慶典？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡有好多檔口，遊戲和好吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,還有我們回去鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能說，是賽蓮的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,組曲光之美少女 第25話\N發現賽蓮的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們和諧的力量在你心裡產生共鳴吧
